lead_paragraph: Wayne Selden Jr. was tired of driving into the teeth of the Kentucky defense and getting his shot swatted away, so the Kansas guard decided in overtime to dunk no matter who got in his way.

headline.print_headline: Selden Leads No. 4 Kansas Past No. 20 Kentucky 90-84 in OT
